com.cyberfront.crdt.operations

Class GenericOperationManager<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.operations.OperationManager
      • com.cyberfront.crdt.operations.GenericOperationManager<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The generic type to manage. The type will need to be annotated to support Jackson serializing as a JSON object. See com.cyberfront.crdt.unittest.data.AbstractDataType for an example of this annotation. Also, the type T should have a constructor which accepts no arguments.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<OperationManager>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimOperationManager

    public class GenericOperationManager<T>
extends OperationManager
    The Class GenericOperationManager provides a mechanism for managing java types as a CRDT by wrapping an object by a collection of operations on that object.
